=3D"docs-internal-guid-a93d33e1-7fff-c8d8-847b-19332e79f54e"><h2>How to Con=
vert Lumens to Watts&nbsp;</h2><p style=3D"text-align: justify;">To convert=
 lumens to watts, the key is to understand the luminous efficiency of diffe=
rent bulb types. Generally speaking, traditional incandescent bulbs produce=
 about 10-15 lumens per watt, while LED lights are much more efficient, usu=
ally producing 80-100 lumens per watt.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"text-alig=
n: justify;">It=E2=80=99s also important to find the luminous efficacy. Her=
e is reference standard values.&nbsp;<br><br></p><ul style=3D"padding-inlin=
